verse.lines:
You saved my soul when I was lost
You've surely been good to me;
You saved my soul when I was lost
You've surely been good to me;
You saved my soul when I was lost
You've surely been good to me;
You have done what this world
  could not do.

Lord Jesus Christ
You've surely been good to me;
Lord Jesus Christ
You've surely been good to me;
Lord Jesus Christ
You've surely been good to me;
You have done what this world
  could not do.

You filled me with the Holy Ghost,
You've surely been good to me;
You filled me with the Holy Ghost,
You've surely been good to me;
You filled me with the Holy Ghost,
You've surely been good to me;
You have done what this world
  could not do.

You healed my body when I was sick,
You've surely been good to me;
You healed my body when I was sick,
You've surely been good to me;
You healed my body when I was sick,
You've surely been good to me;
You have done what this world
  could not do.
